attributes.Title: Inception
attributes.Stars: Leonardo DiCaprio, Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Elliot Page
attributes.Description: A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O., but his tragic past may doom the project and his team to disaster.

attributes.Title: Fight Club
attributes.Stars: Brad Pitt, Edward Norton, Meat Loaf
attributes.Description: An insomniac office worker and a devil-may-care soap maker form an underground fight club that evolves into much more.

attributes.Title: WALLÂ·E
attributes.Writers: Andrew Stanton, Pete Docter, Jim Reardon
attributes.Stars: Ben Burtt, Elissa Knight, Jeff Garlin
attributes.Description: In the distant future, a small waste-collecting robot inadvertently embarks on a space journey that will ultimately decide the fate of mankind.

attributes.Title: Psycho
attributes.Stars: Anthony Perkins, Janet Leigh, Vera Miles
attributes.Description: A Phoenix secretary embezzles $40,000 from her employer's client, goes on the run and checks into a remote motel run by a young man under the domination of his mother.

attributes.Title: Alien
attributes.Writers: Dan O'Bannon (screenplay by), Ronald Shusett (story by)
attributes.Stars: Sigourney Weaver, Tom Skerritt, John Hurt
attributes.Description: The crew of a commercial spacecraft encounter a deadly lifeform after investigating an unknown transmission.

attributes.Title: American Beauty
attributes.Stars: Kevin Spacey, Annette Bening, Thora Birch
attributes.Description: A sexually frustrated suburban father has a mid-life crisis after becoming infatuated with his daughter's best friend.

attributes.Title: City of God
attributes.Stars: Alexandre Rodrigues, Leandro Firmino, Matheus Nachtergaele
attributes.Description: In the slums of Rio, two kids' paths diverge as one struggles to become a photographer and the other a kingpin.

attributes.Title: The Silence of the Lambs
attributes.Stars: Jodie Foster, Anthony Hopkins, Scott Glenn
attributes.Description: A young F.B.I. cadet must receive the help of an incarcerated and manipulative cannibal killer to help catch another serial killer, a madman who skins his victims.

attributes.Title: Apocalypse Now
attributes.Writers: John Milius, Francis Ford Coppola, Michael Herr
attributes.Stars: Martin Sheen, Marlon Brando, Robert Duvall
attributes.Description: A U.S. Army officer serving in Vietnam is tasked with assassinating a renegade Special Forces Colonel who sees himself as a god.

attributes.Title: The Godfather
attributes.Stars: Marlon Brando, Al Pacino, James Caan
attributes.Description: The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty in postwar New York City transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant youngest son.

attributes.Title: Casablanca
attributes.Writers: Julius J. Epstein, Philip G. Epstein, Howard Koch
attributes.Stars: Humphrey Bogart, Ingrid Bergman, Paul Henreid
attributes.Description: A cynical expatriate American cafe owner struggles to decide whether or not to help his former lover and her fugitive husband escape the Nazis in French Morocco.

attributes.Title: The Prestige
attributes.Writers: Jonathan Nolan (screenplay), Christopher Nolan (screenplay), Christopher Priest (novel)
attributes.Stars: Christian Bale, Hugh Jackman, Scarlett Johansson
attributes.Description: After a tragic accident, two stage magicians in 1890s London engage in a battle to create the ultimate illusion while sacrificing everything they have to outwit each other.

attributes.Title: Django Unchained
attributes.Stars: Jamie Foxx, Christoph Waltz, Leonardo DiCaprio
attributes.Description: With the help of a German bounty-hunter, a freed slave sets out to rescue his wife from a brutal plantation-owner in Mississippi.

attributes.Title: Interstellar
attributes.Stars: Matthew McConaughey, Anne Hathaway, Jessica Chastain
attributes.Description: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.

attributes.Title: It's a Wonderful Life
attributes.Writers: Frances Goodrich, Albert Hackett, Frank Capra
attributes.Stars: James Stewart, Donna Reed, Lionel Barrymore
attributes.Description: An angel is sent from Heaven to help a desperately frustrated businessman by showing him what life would have been like if he had never existed.
